duck: Complete (News from Babel album) - Complete is a three-CD box set by the English avant-rock band News from Babel.
complete definition: having all necessary parts, elements, or steps.
To be complete is to be in the state of requiring nothing else to be added.
Complete (The Smiths album) - Complete is a box set released by British band The Smiths.
Completeness - In general, an object is complete if nothing needs to be added to it.
To be complete is to be in the state of requiring nothing else to be added.
Complete (Lila McCann album) - Complete is the third album by country music artist Lila McCann.
